At my department we use Google Desktop Search heavily. Sadly - JIRA can not be searched with the Google Desktop Search. No current plugin will work with it.

Is anyone working on a GDS plugin to be able to search JIRA? This would be *most* welcome - we currently are able to search both personal- and groupmail, local- and networkdisks, and out Wiki system. Adding JIRA to this would be *very* useful.

